---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Privacy Policy - Coe Code" description="Privacy policy for Coe Code applications and services.">
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 pt-12 pb-16">
    <!-- Page Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">
        Privacy <span class="text-yellow-400">Policy</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-white/70 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Your privacy is important to us. This policy explains how we handle your data.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Privacy Content -->
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 p-8 mb-8">
        <p class="text-sm text-white/60 mb-6">Last updated: June 2023</p>
        
        <div class="space-y-8 text-white/80">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Our Commitment to Privacy</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              At Coe Code, we believe privacy is a fundamental right. This privacy policy explains how we 
              collect, use, and protect your information when you use our applications and services.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Information We Collect</h2>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-white">Linc App</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Linc is designed with privacy as a core principle. All your relationship data is stored 
              locally on your device and is never transmitted to our servers or any third parties.
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Contact information you choose to add (stored locally only)</li>
              <li>Interaction history you record (stored locally only)</li>
              <li>App preferences and settings (stored locally only)</li>
              <li>No personal data is collected by Coe Code servers</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3 text-white">Website Analytics</h3>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Our website may collect basic analytics information to help us improve our services:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Page views and site navigation patterns</li>
              <li>Device type and browser information</li>
              <li>General geographic location (country/region level)</li>
              <li>No personally identifiable information is collected</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Since Linc stores all data locally on your device, we don't have access to your personal 
              information. The limited analytics data we collect from our website is used solely to:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Improve our website experience</li>
              <li>Understand how our applications are being used</li>
              <li>Provide customer support when requested</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Data Sharing</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. We do not 
              share your information except in the following limited circumstances:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mt-4">
              <li>When required by law or legal process</li>
              <li>To protect our rights or the safety of our users</li>
              <li>With your explicit consent</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Data Security</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              Your data in Linc is protected by your device's built-in security features, including 
              device passcodes and biometric authentication. We recommend keeping your device 
              secure and up to date.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Your Rights</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Since Linc stores all data locally on your device, you have complete control over 
              your information:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>You can delete any data at any time within the app</li>
              <li>You can export your data using the app's backup features</li>
              <li>Uninstalling the app will remove all associated data from your device</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Children's Privacy</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              Our applications are not designed for or directed at children under 13. We do not 
              knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any 
              significant changes by posting a notice on our website or within our applications.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Contact Us</h2>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">
              If you have any questions about this privacy policy or our privacy practices, 
              please contact us:
            </p>
            <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-lg p-4 border border-white/10">
              <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:privacy@coecode.io" class="text-yellow-400 hover:text-yellow-300">privacy@coecode.io</a></p>
              <p><strong>Address:</strong> Coe Code LLC, Missoula, Montana, USA</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Navigation Links -->
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-white/10">
      <a 
        href="/" 
        class="px-6 py-3 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 rounded-lg transition-colors"
      >
        Home
      </a>
      <a 
        href="/linc" 
        class="px-6 py-3 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 rounded-lg transition-colors"
      >
        Linc
      </a>
      <a 
        href="/connect" 
        class="px-6 py-3 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 rounded-lg transition-colors"
      >
        Contact Us
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout> 